data.eml:eml: A new species of Hypsiboas Wagler (Anura: Hylidae) closely related to H. multifasciatus Günther from southeastern Brazil

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Carvalho, Thiago Ribeiro De, Giaretta, Ariovaldo Antonio, Facure, Kátia Gomes (2010): A new species of Hypsiboas Wagler (Anura: Hylidae) closely related to H. multifasciatus Günther from southeastern Brazil.
